*** 20090829 Version 0.9.2 ***

- TCP support
- configurable internal timeout (socket/poll)
- Cherokee handler
- code refactoring
- Makefiles
- customizable harakiri handler (put an harakiri(environ, start_response) function in your wsgi script)
